Class DataNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.rmi.server.RemoteObject
      • java.rmi.server.RemoteServer
        • java.rmi.server.UnicastRemoteObject
          • dfs.DataNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataNodeInterface, java.io.Serializable, java.rmi.Remote

    public class DataNode
extends java.rmi.server.UnicastRemoteObject
implements DataNodeInterface
    This class is the main thread to start a data node in DFS. It provides remote services for name nodes and clients to upload, query data.
